PERFORM TEST
DEFINE SUBROUTINE TEST
RD1. READ (30) EMPLOYEES BY PERSONNEL-ID
  DISPLAY *ISN PERSONNEL-ID FIRST-NAME
*
  FD1. FIND EMPLOYEES WITH PERSONNEL-ID = PERSONNEL-ID(RD1.)
    IF NO RECORDS FOUND
    DO
      WRITE 'NOT FOUND'
      ESCAPE BOTTOM
    DOEND
    IF FIRST-NAME = 'REINER'
    DO
      WRITE 'NAME' FIRST-NAME
      DELETE(FD1.)
      END TRANSACTION
    DOEND
*   LOOP  /* NATURAL OK WITHOUT THIS LINE 
LOOP  (RD1.)
END-SUBROUTINE
End
